metadata.title: DPM Dar, UAE Minister discuss ways strengthen bilateral ties

content.article_body: ISLAMABAD, Jul 18 (APP): Deputy Prime Minister and Foreign Minister, Senator Mohammad Ishaq Dar on Friday spoke with the Minister of State of the United Arab Emirates (UAE), Ahmed Ali Al Sayegh. They discussed ways to further strengthen the Pakistan-UAE ties and enhance bilateral economic cooperation, a press statement issued by the Foreign Office Spokesperson said.
